query: SELECT date_trunc($1, collected_at) "collected_at: NaiveDateTime", cast(sum(upload_diff) AS bigint) upload, cast(sum(download_diff) AS bigint) download FROM vpn_session_stats JOIN vpn_client_session s ON session_id = s.id WHERE collected_at >= $2 AND s.location_id = $3 GROUP BY 1 ORDER BY 1 LIMIT $4
